        <p>15+ year advertising as a leader in global digital.</p>
        <p>saidediaw2010@yahoo.com; Tel:772655486</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="column">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="assets/Photo(2).jpeg" alt="Astou" style="width:100%">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Astou Ndiaye</h2>
        <p class="title">Secretary</p>
        <p>Coordination with all the clients around the word.</p>
        <p>astou@example.com; Tel:772195026</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="column">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="assets/Photo(1).jpeg" alt="car park" style="width:100%">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Car Park</h2>
        <p class="title">Car Park</p>
        <p>All cars for you.</p>
        <p>car@example.com; Tel:779571726</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
